4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for those with no prior experience. The 16-week program includes three live online classes each week, with a maximum class size of 18 students. Participants will develop a foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp also covers risk management, compliance with international standards, and concludes with an official completion certificate. Classes are available in both English and Spanish, depending on the campus. For more details, visit [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop